              <path d="M12 8v1M12 12v4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong>AI Use Declaration:</strong> if you used AI at any point, you complete
              the AI Use Declaration at the end of the assessment document. List the tools
