          <h2>Lessons 2 &amp; 3: Work Time on the Internal</h2>

          <p class="section-intro">
            This is a double, so you have around 100 minutes of supervised writing time.
            Three quick bits of housekeeping first, then it's heads-down on the report.
          </p>


          <!-- ── Item 1: Textbook Site Access ── -->
